  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0da7\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0daf\u0dc5 \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dd6 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The tusked elephant goes on its last journey after losing the battle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Anuradhapura Wildlife Veterinary Officer Mr. Chandana Jayasinghe said that the elephant king Maheshakhya, who lost a duel with an elephant and fell in a field, had one of his tusks cut off by a herd.",
        "The elephant king who was defeated in a duel fell in a paddy field in Kabithigollewa Thittagonewa Moraoya, and according to a notification from the local residents, the wildlife veterinarians started treatment.",
        "While receiving treatment for about 20 days, the previous day, some savior had cut off a tusk of this elephant king by hitting him with an ax.",
        "Veterinarians also say that this elephant, who was seriously ill, died this morning.",
        "Dr. Chandana Jayasinghe says that the elephant was treated continuously for almost 20 days."
      ],
